# Django Student Management System

This project is a web-based student management system built with Django. It is designed to help you learn about Django models, views, templates, and admin features.

## Features
- Add, update, and delete student records
- User-friendly web interface
- Django admin integration
- Organized codebase for easy extension

## Folder Structure
- `core/`: Main app logic
- `static/`: Static files (CSS, JS, images)
- `student_mgmt/`: Project settings and configuration

## How to Use
1. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt` (if available)
2. Run migrations: `python manage.py migrate`
3. Start the server: `python manage.py runserver`
4. Access the app at `http://127.0.0.1:8000/`

## Learning Outcomes
- Work with Django models and admin
- Build CRUD web apps
- Practice Django project organization

